&lt;p&gt;
The mRNA produced by the  &lt;i&gt;cspA&lt;/i&gt; gene has been observed mainly in the poles of the cell [&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/31540875&quot;&gt;Kannaiah19&lt;/a&gt;].</comment>
